                                                                                                <div class="art-postcontent clearfix"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Welcome to the Black Cultural Centre for Nova Scotia&#8217;s website.</span></p>
<p>Established in 1983, to Protect, Preserve and Promote the history and culture of African Nova Scotians. The Centre is a museum and cultural gathering place, were the rich history of Nova Scotians of African Descent can be discovered and explored.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Be Inspired!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><div class="easyRotatorWrapper" align="center">

